node.title: Multiple people injured as SUV ploughs through Christmas parade in Wisconsin
node.alt: A red car speeds through down a parade.
node.description: More than 20 people have been injured after an SUV sped through a Christmas parade in Waukesha, Wisconsin.
node.content: ["More than 20 people are being treated for injuries after a SUV was driven into a Christmas parade in Wisconsin, local police say.", "The incident happened in the town of\u00a0Waukesha, about 30 kilometres outside Milwaukee.", "Local police chief\u00a0Dan Thompson said the vehicle had been recovered and there were no further threats.", "\"A red SUV drove into our Christmas parade that we were holding downtown. More than 20 individuals were injured as a result of this incident,\" he said.", "Authorities have identified a person of interest in the case, he added, without giving further details.", "He said some of the injured were taken to hospital by ambulance, others by police and still more by family and friends.", "More to come.", "ABC/wires"]
